name: Marlyn Garcia
description: o say that I’m just young and beautiful girl, it says nothing about me. I’m many sided person. I hope a lot of interests. The way to a man’s heart is through his stomach, so I hope I will find this way to my man, because I can cook very well. My inner world is very various. I like music, movies, sport. Also I’m interested in fashion and stile, my dream to be designer. I think I can be very interesting for my man. I love to meet new people and communicate with them about new things My character is perfect! No, truly, I’m very easy-going and friendly girl! Wink I like to smile, to be in high spirits and inspire everything around. I’m reliable and trustworthy; I’m a very good friend: patient, attentive and optimistic. My positive energy makes my life interesting and beautiful. I would like to share it with my beloved man. I haven’t found my beloved yet, he must be somewhere here, I feel it! Maybe, it’s you?
